  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Geo-blocking of online content after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How restricting access to online content (geo-blocking) between the UK and EU will be regulated if there’s a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

